From 16d8aaf3865588a323b04d281985bd8daf569daf Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Moritz Mack <mmack@apache.org>
Date: Thu, 9 Jan 2025 08:57:47 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Strengthen encryption for elasticsearch-keystore tool to AES
 256 (#119749)

The latest format version (7) of KeyStoreWrapper will be using a 256
bits key for the AES cipher.

Closes #ES-10419
